1276
01:19:54,300 --> 01:19:58,832
(woman speaking Vietnamese)

1277
01:19:58,932 --> 01:20:02,100
The day's operation burned down 150 houses,

1278
01:20:02,199 --> 01:20:05,432
wounded three women, killed one baby,

1279
