Dear Mum and Dad,

1336
01:23:39,966 --> 01:23:43,033
I am now with the 1st Brigade,
101st Airborne Division

1337
01:23:43,132 --> 01:23:44,932
in Vietnam.

1338
01:23:45,033 --> 01:23:47,865
("The War Drags On" by Donovan playing)

1339
01:23:51,033 --> 01:23:52,865
