01:25:00,899 --> 01:25:02,832
GALLOWAY: We were all
excited about the arrival

1359
01:25:02,932 --> 01:25:07,565
of the 1st Cavalry Division,
an experimental unit.

1360
01:25:07,666 --> 01:25:11,865
